Status

Dependencies
------------

Imports forgetSQL

All other imports are either python builtins or modules located in
the devicemanagement directory.


Installation
------------

All the files should be placed in a directory 'status'' in the
webroot.

The file StatusTemplate.tmpl must be compiled by cheetah and put in the
'status' directory.

The file 'htaccess' must be renamed to '.htaccess'. The path directive in
the htaccess file must possibly be edited. The last element points to the
status directory in the webroot.

**MIDLERTIDIG**: filen 'default-prefs.pickle' må kopieres til et sted pythoninterpreteren har skrivetilgang (/tmp på isbre) og full path må sette is toppen
av StatusPrefs.py (DEFAULT_PREFS_FILENAME). Skulle vært i db selvfølgelig, sorry.
